data.description: Great horse property with Spacious Family home on 14 acres! Features 8-10 stalls, barn, large storage room with 1 car garage! 5 electric fenced pastures w/shelters. Home feature 5 bedrooms on main level w/new carpet. Upstairs family room w/office & skylights possible 6th bedroom. Primary suite w/full bath on  main. Living room features wood stove, laminate floors, dining area & large window. Kitchen has small eating bar, dishwasher. Spacious deck for entertaining. Irrigation on the front pasture, sprinklers, laundry room, solar panels.
